About Tapas My work: Tour Operator &Guide
Lives in Sylhet District, Bangladesh
Hey hello, this is Tapas, have been a tour guide since 2009 for Sreemangal and around Bangladesh. With a passion for tourism, I am here to make your stay unforgettable. Having traveled to multiple countries, I know how to offer top-notch guest services. I'll gladly recommend the best tourist hotspots in Sreemangal and around. So come on over and let me show you the time of your life!
